Detailed Description

template<typename EvalT, typename Traits>
class LCM::ThermoMechanicalStress< EvalT, Traits >

ThermoMechanical stress response.

This evaluator computes stress based on a uncoupled Neohookean Helmholtz potential with temperature dependence
